{
  "texts": [
    " Many machine learning algorithms are sensitive to the scale of features, requiring careful normalization or standardization.",
    "(c) Deep Learning ApproachIt is powerful approach that involves training neural networks on large datasets to perform tasks.",
    "In the context of NER, a deep learning (DL) [8], [76] approach uses neural networks to automatically identify and classify entities such as names of people, locations, organizations within a given data.",
    "In it, the input text converts into numerical representation that can be processed by neural networks.",
    "The network learns to extract meaningful features from the text data, focusing on linguistic patterns then it attaches a tagging layer to the network's output."
  ]
}